{
  "title": "Rich Russian Rice Krispies Pilaf",
  "description": "A kid-friendly, low-calorie Russian dish featuring Rice Krispies, cooked to perfection using sous-vide technology. This rich and crumbly pilaf is a twist on traditional Russian cuisine.",
  "cuisine": "Russian",
